data.description:
2 5/8% ASSUMABLE MTG. AMAZING SOLAR home situated on a N/S PREMIUM LOT with a GREEN BELT next door. This home has it all - 3 Bed, 2.5 Baths, breakfast room, den + 3 car garage! You are greeted by beautiful curb appeal w/mature landscaping & SPECTACULAR PALM TREES. Step inside the iron gate into a HUGE TRAVERTINE COURTYARD which leads you inside to an open floor plan w/12 ft SOARING CEILINGS & lots of windows w/PLANTATION SHUTTERS thru-out home. Living room/family room have
wood floors & are separated by a GAS FIREPLACE. Also a new STUNNING CUSTOM LIGHTED ENTERTAINMENT UNIT - perfect for your 75'' TV. GOURMET kitchen features: white raised panel staggered cabinets, SS refrigerator, GAS COOKTOP, wall oven & microwave, DESIGNER backsplash & CUSTOM vented HOOD. Large Owner's Suite is the perfect retreat - sitting area for reading, door to the patio, two closets, bath is spa-like w/soaking tub, granite c-tops, separate vanities, SNAIL SHOWER w/an IMPRESSIVE vanity &  chandelier! Two other bedrooms along with a Jack & Jill bathroom are perfect for when company visits. Den is in a private wing w/double French doors to the courtyard. Step outside to a SOUTH FACING backyard oasis w/lush landscaping, huge covered patio, fully-fenced, cascading water feature, custom TV wall, gas firepit, synthetic grass, misters, awnings, landscape lights, stone accents & GORGEOUS flower pots! Additional Upgrades: newer HVAC SYSTEM, cabinets in garage, epoxy floors, water softener, reverse osmosis & custom lighting. Don't miss the opportunity to call this home!
